				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey guys, 
<br />

<br />
Im curious as to whether any of you guys use game pads to make twisting songs easier.  I know ive had on occasion some pain in my wrists from twisting for hours on end.
<br />

<br />
I know it has helped some other classes, rangers, pallys'etc. but what do you guys recommend?
<br />

<br />
Tulban Unseelie
<br />
65 Maestro
<br />
Vazaelle</span></td>
